#: converter/forms.py:9
msgid "Incluir arquivos de pseudopotencial (.psf) no download"
msgstr "Include pseudopotential files (.psf) in download"

#: converter/forms.py:13
msgid ""
"Se marcado, o download será um arquivo .zip contendo o .fdf e os arquivos ."
"psf necessários."
msgstr ""
"If checked, the download will be a .zip file containing the .fdf "
"and the required .psf files."

#: converter/forms.py:19
